{
  "stem": "1641.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And that was exactly the reason why Hitler ordered our head of state to let the German army come in, because the Hungarian army couldn't-- obviously couldn't hold back the Russians.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So the Germans came in to take up the positions on the border.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Well-- well, at that time I had to do part-time labor service.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "All the Jewish young men had to do, irrespective of age.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "From 15 to 20, we had to-- after the bombing attacks, when the English and American bombs, we were called out immediately.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We had to come at 3 o'clock in the morning, or 5 o'clock in the morning, help with the long hoses to put out the fires.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Because if 500-- 500 bombers come, they cause a fair bit of damage.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And all the big factories were burning.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And the oil refineries were burning.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But that was just part time, only after bombing attacks, which happened three, four times a week.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And then, of course, all the usual laws come out-- came out.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "You have to put on your yellow star.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Anybody who is caught with the-- with the Christians, especial-- especially sexual relationship, that's immediately heavy-- heavy jail for that, if you are mixing with a non-Jew.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And so that-- that was only three or four weeks went past.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And then everybody in my-- in my year was called up for full-time forced labor-- I mean, labor-- labor camp.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Some of the labor camp work was in Hungary.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And lot of others were sent out, of course, to Russia, to-- mostly to pick-- collect mines, minefields.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I was very lucky.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- I was not sent to Russia, in the first few weeks, anyhow.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
